**Verifying Implementation Details**

I'm now implementing the `showAnalysisPanel` state within `App.tsx` along with the associated `handleOpenReport` function. I've also added the "Report" button to the toolbar, which triggers the analysis and displays the full report. My focus is on the correct visibility control. I've confirmed that the existing PDF generation is robust and will maintain this behavior. I've ensured a `ClipboardList` is added to my imports.


